{
  "stem": "2118.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Here was an army where nobody marched.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Everybody was sitting either in a car or on a truck with mounted machine guns with double barrel, which I've never seen in my life, with cannons mounted on-- on-- on half tracks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They even had steamrollers to straighten the street after the army marched.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They had field kitchens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When they stopped, they served rice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We used to believe that the Germans don't have enough food, because they put everything in armament.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They're starving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Or they used to say the slogan, armament instead of body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They had plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The-- the Army looked clean, shaved, dressed, with cameras, taking pictures like tourists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were glum.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The Poles were glum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were some Germans who already had German flags.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They bought flowers for the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They already had the [INAUDIBLE] and the arm band.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And-- and some German flags were already flying from some buildings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And that army marched all day long without interruption, from morning till late, till I don't know when.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Till I went to sleep, that was still-- you could still hear them marching.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The noise was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It wasn't marching by foot, it was marching by equipment, by-- by tanks and by trucks and by-- I don't know, you name it, they had.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I have never seen an army like this till I saw the American equipment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it changed instantly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It changed up so the-- the-- the-- the fear preceded them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was a boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't understand that much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's the way-- when I think back, that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were already afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People already knew that nothing good, especially Jewish people, that nothing good came out of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
